 Description:   This proc populates table dbo.sa_Finance_MortgageDetail. This is the staging table
				for table dbo.owt_Finance_MortgageDetail which is populated by another stored proc.
				
				It is called as follows:

				exec dbo.owp_Finance_MortgageDetail_Staging 'Openwork', 'Finance 2016'
									
