Date created:	05/10/2016

		Type:	Financial Reporting 2016
		
 Description:   This proc populates table dbo.owt_Finance_SOBacsDateNull from table
				logi.FinstatReporting22SONullBacsDate the original proof-of-concept table.
				
				It is called as follows:

				exec dbo.owp_Finance_SOBacsDateNull_1Off_2 'Openwork', 'Finance 2016'
									
