 Description:   This proc populates table owt_Finance_StatementCommMarg from table
				logi.FinstatReporting7StatementCommMarg the original proof-of-concept table.
				
				It is called as follows:

				exec owp_Finance_StatementCommMarg_1Off 'Openwork', 'Finance 2016'
									
Amendment History								
