/****************************************************************************
     Program:	owp_HeadOfficeUsersFromActiveDirectory         
      Author:	A Groves
Date created:	01/11/2010              
                      
Description:	This proc calls proc sp_OWUtil_ActiveDirectoryReader to
				populate table msct_HeadOfficeUsers.  It replaces a C# Moore
				Stephens utility (TestRig) during the ACS to Rackspace Migration.

				This proc would be called as follows:

					exec owp_HeadOfficeUsersFromActiveDirectory 'Openwork', 'ActiveDirectory'
          
        
  Amendment History               
  -----------------               
                      
  Date			Who			Description       
  ----			---			-----------     
  14/01/2011	A Groves	Added extra parameter to enable further parameters
							to be derived to remove hardcoding that then enables
							this proc to run ina all environments: DEV/UAT/PROD.
  31/01/2011	A Groves	This is a new version that completely supercedes the
							changes of 14/01/2011. A new version of the AD Reader
							utility (Utilities..sp_OWUtil_ActiveDirectoryReader)
							has been created with 100% of the hardcoding removed.
							The AD organisation unit (OU) hardcoding has been 
							removed altogether and the AD Domain details have been
							set up as conig data on table "mst_DataImportConfiguration" 
****************************************************************************/
